dcterms:description: A dataset containing vehicle traffic flow data collected on Highway 2A in Canada, recorded hourly over a period of three weeks, which is used to analyze vehicle density based on the Lighthill-Whitham-Richards model.
dcterms:title: Highway Vehicle Traffic Flow Trace

dcterms:creator: J. Zhang

dcterms:description: A dataset that collects GPS traces of taxis in urban areas of Xi’an, China, over a period of three weeks, used to analyze vehicle density and traffic patterns.
dcterms:title: Urban Vehicle Traffic Flow Trace
